description:
Thank you, Tampines. It has been a wonderful six-year journey.

We will always cherish the support you have shown us, particularly during the challenging times of the Covid-19 pandemic, and how you all rallied around us after hearing about our imminent closure.

It has been our utmost pleasure to serve you happy food.

Farewell! üëãüèº

We‚Äôre ever so grateful to see all your faces come by our little store to get a scoop as we count down the last few days we‚Äôll be at Our Tampines Hub üíô T-5 days now. Come down if you can, we‚Äôd love to serve you one last time.

description:
While we‚Äôre still processing and waiting for when the last day of Merely Sunshine will be, it is with deep sadness to share that Merely at Our Tampines Hub will be closing for good on 18 June Sunday.

When it rains it pours. We had wished to remain and continue serving our customers in the East, but was informed a few days ago that we lost on the public tender to renew our lease.

It‚Äôs been our honour to scoop and serve balls of happiness to you the past 11 years. Your patronage, kind words, and enthusiasm has been everything that has kept us going. 

Till the last day of Merely Sunshine is firmed up. We guess this is probably Thank you and Goodbye. 

So thank you, each and every one of you, from the bottom of our hearts. Maybe till the next time then? üç¶
caption: Photo by Merely Ice Cream in Merely at Our Tampines Hub.
